### Library list
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Book detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Page indexes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/pages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### First page
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/pages/0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Out-of-range page → 404 page_not_found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/pages/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Save progress at page 5
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "lastPageIdx": 5 }

###

### Negative progress → 400 validation_failed
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "lastPageIdx": -1 }

###

### Progress >= pageCount → 400 invalid_progress
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "lastPageIdx": 999999 }

###

### Foreign book → 404 (404 not 403 so existence is hidden)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
